M;The Stock Exchange Taurus paperless settlement system will cost #50m.andM;- o -andM;ABB Metrawatt Ltd of Cheltenham, formed a year ago to sell the Austrian madeAsea Brown Boveri AG line of colour thermal printers and Porsche-designed penplotters in the UK, has signed a distribution partnership agreement with HighWycombe-based systems distributor Rapid Recall Ltd: ABB claims to be theworld's largest manufacturer of pen plotters for the OEM market.andM;- o -andM;Seymour Cray has been talking about his new Cray Computer Corp venture,reports Supercomputing Review, saying &quot;It's really a nice simple proposition- we have a year-and-a-half and we either win or lose&quot;; and what does heenjoy most about the new venture? &quot;I enjoy the pessimism of the rest of theworld.&quot;andO;</TEXT></DOC>